    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/45208401/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u45208401-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/45208401/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">angulo</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-12-27"
      class="main-meta">2014-12-27 21:19:52</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7294279_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  布克哈特的这本书虽说是演讲集，但是里面所讲的内容对于我这位对希腊历史不太了解的人而言，大有醍醐灌顶和视野顿开之感。他的见解十分的新颖，自由思想和独立的看法在文中随处可见。 对于希腊历史，我知道不多，看完后，我逐渐的明白了原来伟大、光荣的古希腊文明竟然也有着如...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            上海人民出版社2012版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7294279_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7294279_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










